title: Mickey Finn (Aussie) - Mickey Finn (1980) [FLAC]
description:
Mickey Finn - Mickey Finn (1980) LP

Genre: Aussie, Hard Rock

Mickey Finn evolved from some legendary bands - Levi Clefs and Fraternity - and is probably one of the most underrated Aussie bands of all time.
